---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="Piattaforme Kubernetes · EKS & Bare-Metal"
  descripcion="Kubernetes su EKS e bare-metal con ArgoCD GitOps, Helm e observability integrata. Deployment di cluster pronti per la produzione in qualsiasi ambiente."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #0A2540;">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-40" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(147,184,255,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 28px 28px;"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 sm:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6" style="background: rgba(30,111,255,0.15); color: #93b8ff; border: 1px solid rgba(30,111,255,0.3);">
          Piattaforme Kubernetes
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-5" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
          Cluster Kubernetes pronti per la produzione dal primo giorno.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl" style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.8);">
          Da EKS su AWS ai cluster bare-metal, forniamo piattaforme Kubernetes guidate da GitOps con ArgoCD, Helm e observability completa integrata.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CAPABILITIES -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">Provisioning EKS</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">Kubernetes gestito su AWS con EKS. Node group, IRSA e Cluster Autoscaler come codice — nessuna configurazione manuale tramite la console.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">ArgoCD GitOps</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">Continuous delivery tramite ArgoCD con sincronizzazione automatica, prune e self-heal. Git è l'unica fonte di verità per lo stato del cluster.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">Gestione Helm chart</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">Deployment di applicazioni con Helm chart e overlay Kustomize. Separazione netta tra configurazione base e valori specifici per ambiente.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">Kubernetes Bare-Metal</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">Cluster Kubernetes on-premise con kubeadm o k3s. Configurazioni production-ready senza dipendenze cloud per workload sensibili.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">Stack di observability</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">Prometheus, Grafana e Alertmanager integrati dal primo giorno. Dashboard e alert per la salute del cluster, le performance e l'utilizzo delle risorse.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">Rete & Sicurezza</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">NetworkPolicy, RBAC e Pod Security Standards come codice. Ingress controller con terminazione TLS e rate limiting configurati fin dall'inizio.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background: #0A2540;" class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Pronto per una piattaforma Kubernetes in produzione?</h2>
      <p class="text-base mb-8" style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.8);">Iniziamo con una valutazione della tua attuale infrastruttura container e creiamo un piano di migrazione concreto.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold text-white" style="background: #1E6FFF;">
        Contattaci
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
